Package net.proteusframework.core.io

Input & Output related utilities.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EntityUtilWriter
    PrintWriter with added methods for outputting entity encoded data.
    FileDeleter
    Helper to delete files.
    NullInputStream
    An empty InputStream.
    NullOutputStream
    The NullOutputStream subclass throws away all output written to it.
    NullReader
    An empty Reader.
    NullWriter
    An empty Writer.
    StreamUtils
    Utilities for dealing with InputStream and OutputStream objects.
    TeeOutputStream
    The TeeOutputStream writes all data written to it to two other OutputStream objects.
    TeeWriter
    The TeeWriter writes all data written to it to two other Writer objects.
    UUEncodeInputStream
    Uudecodes an ASCII byte stream using the base64 method.
    UUEncodeOutputStream
    Uuencodes an 8-bit stream using the base64 method.
